metadata.name: Sea Cliffs of Molokai
metadata.description:
"The greatness of a community is most accurately measured by the compassionate actions of its members." – Coretta Scott King

The Sea Cliffs of Molokai is an Edition Collection of 50 pieces whose sole purpose is to feed its profits back into the community through acquiring NFT Art from up and coming artists throughout the space!

A part of the growing photo documentary of a Blackhawk Pilot created by Christopher Howell
